-a-wide-swath-of-the-country/">the geographic aspect</a> of the investment boom that&#39;s resulting from the US&#39; new industrial policy.考虑到 2016 年特朗普在中西部地区取得突破性胜利后引起的热烈讨论，你可能会认为投资会集中在那里。但事实上，南部和西部的收入越来越多，而且相对于 GDP 而言，南部所占的份额过大： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F8f9f64cb-7e68-4e42-82b8-2011c91b45ab_768x635.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F8f9f64cb-7e68-4e42-82b8-2011c91b45ab_768x635.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F8f9f64cb-7e68-4e42-82b8-2011c91b45ab_768x635.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F8f9f64cb-7e68-4e42-82b8-2011c91b45ab_768x635.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F8f9f64cb-7e68-4e42-82b8-2011c91b45ab_768x635.jpeg" width="666" height="550.6640625" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/8f9f64cb-7e68-4e42-82b8-2011c91b45ab_768x635.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:635,&quot;width&quot;:768,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:666,&quot;bytes&quot;:72605,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;int